#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"KIO S3 is a KIO worker that allows you to browse and manage files stored in "
"Amazon S3 and S3-compatible storage services (such as Cloudflare R2, "
"DigitalOcean Spaces, MinIO, and others) directly from <application>Dolphin</"
"application> and other KDE applications."
msgstr ""
"KIO S3 je program za obdelavo podatkov KIO, ki vam omogoča brskanje in "
"upravljanje datotek, shranjenih v storitvah za shranjevanje Amazon S3 in S3-"
"združljivih storitvah (kot so Cloudflare R2, DigitalOcean Spaces, MinIO in "
"druge), neposredno iz aplikacije <application>Dolphin</application> in "
"drugih aplikacij KDE."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "With KIO S3, you can:"
msgstr "S KIO S3 lahko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse buckets and folders"
msgstr "Brskate po vedrih in mapah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Upload and download files"
msgstr "Prenašate datoteke sem in tja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy, rename, and delete files and folders"
msgstr "Kopirate, preimenujete in brišete datoteke in mape"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create folders inside buckets"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje map znotraj veder"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connect to multiple S3-compatible services at the same time using named "
"profiles"
msgstr ""
"Hkrati se povežite z več storitvami, združljivimi s S3, z uporabo "
"poimenovanih profilov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Profiles"
msgstr "Konfigurirate profile"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"KIO S3 supports connecting to multiple S3-compatible storage services "
"through named profiles. Each profile stores the connection settings for one "
"service. You can manage profiles in <menuchoice><guimenu>System Settings</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Network</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>S3 Backends</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"KIO S3 podpira povezovanje z več storitvami za shranjevanje, združljivimi s "
"S3, prek poimenovanih profilov. Vsak profil shrani nastavitve povezave za "
"eno storitev. Profile lahko upravljate v <menuchoice><guimenu>Sistemske "
"nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Omrežje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Zaledni "
"sistemi S3</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a Profile"
msgstr "Dodajanje profila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Add Profile...</guibutton> button and fill in the "
"following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj profil ...</guibutton> in izpolnite naslednja "
"polja:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A descriptive name for this profile (required), &eg; <userinput>My Cloud "
"Storage</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Opisno ime za ta profil (obvezno), npr. <userinput>My Cloud Storage</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Endpoint URL"
msgstr "URL končne točke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The URL of the S3-compatible service, &eg; <userinput>https://s3.example."
"com</userinput>. Leave empty to use the default Amazon S3 endpoint."
msgstr ""
"URL storitve, združljive s S3, npr. <userinput>https://s3.example.com</"
"userinput>. Pustite prazno, če želite uporabiti privzeto končno točko Amazon "
"S3."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Region"
msgstr "Regija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The storage region, &eg; <userinput>us-east-1</userinput> or "
"<userinput>auto</userinput>. Leave empty to use the region from your AWS "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"Regija shranjevanja, npr. <userinput>us-east-1</userinput> ali "
"<userinput>auto</userinput>. Pustite prazno, če želite uporabiti regijo iz "
"vaše konfiguracije AWS."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "AWS Profile"
msgstr "Profil AWS"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the credentials profile from <filename>~/.aws/credentials</"
"filename>. If left empty, the profile identifier is used as the credentials "
"profile name."
msgstr ""
"Ime profila poverilnic iz <filename>~/.aws/credentials</filename>. Če polje "
"pustite prazno, se kot ime profila poverilnic uporabi identifikator profila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use path-style S3 URLs"
msgstr "Uporabi URL-je S3 v slogu poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this for services that do not support virtual-hosted-style "
"addressing, such as MinIO or some Ceph deployments. Most services, including "
"Amazon S3 and Cloudflare R2, do not need this."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči to za storitve, ki ne podpirajo naslavljanja v slogu virtualnega "
"gostovanja, kot sta MinIO ali nekatere uvedbe Ceph. Večina storitev, "
"vključno z Amazon S3 in Cloudflare R2, tega ne potrebuje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After adding a profile, click <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> to save. The new "
"profile will appear as a shortcut in the <application>Dolphin</application> "
"Places panel."
msgstr ""
"Ko dodate profil, kliknite <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>, da ga shranite. "
"Novi profil se bo prikazal kot bližnjica na plošči Mesta v "
"<application>Dolphin</application>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing and Deleting Profiles"
msgstr "Urejanje in brisanje profilov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each profile in the list has an edit and a delete action. Editing opens the "
"same dialog with the current values pre-filled. Deleting asks for "
"confirmation before removing the profile. Remember to click "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton> to save your changes."
msgstr ""
"Vsak profil na seznamu ima dejanje urejanja in brisanja. Urejanje odpre isto "
"pogovorno okno s trenutnimi vnaprej izpolnjenimi vrednostmi. Brisanje "
"zahteva potrditev pred odstranitvijo profila. Ne pozabite klikniti "
"<guibutton>Uveljavi</guibutton>, da shranite spremembe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "AWS Credentials"
msgstr "Poverilnice AWS"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"KIO S3 uses the standard AWS credentials chain to authenticate with S3 "
"services. Credentials are read from <filename>~/.aws/credentials</filename>, "
"which can contain multiple named profiles:"
msgstr ""
"KIO S3 uporablja standardno verigo poverilnic AWS za preverjanje pristnosti "
"s storitvami S3. Poverilnice se berejo iz datoteke <filename>~/.aws/"
"credentials</filename>, ki lahko vsebuje več poimenovanih profilov:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[default]\n"
"aws_access_key_id = YOUR_KEY\n"
"aws_secret_access_key = YOUR_SECRET\n"
"\n"
"[mycloud]\n"
"aws_access_key_id = YOUR_CLOUD_KEY\n"
"aws_secret_access_key = YOUR_CLOUD_SECRET"
msgstr ""
"[default]\n"
"aws_access_key_id = YOUR_KEY\n"
"aws_secret_access_key = YOUR_SECRET\n"
"\n"
"[mycloud]\n"
"aws_access_key_id = YOUR_CLOUD_KEY\n"
"aws_secret_access_key = YOUR_CLOUD_SECRET"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each KIO S3 profile uses the <guilabel>AWS Profile</guilabel> field to "
"select which credentials section to use. For example, a profile with "
"<guilabel>AWS Profile</guilabel> set to <userinput>mycloud</userinput> will "
"use the credentials from the <literal>[mycloud]</literal> section above."
msgstr ""
"Vsak profil KIO S3 uporablja polje <guilabel>AWS Profile</guilabel> za "
"izbiro razdelka s poverilnicami. Na primer, profil z <guilabel>AWS Profile</"
"guilabel>, nastavljenim na <userinput>mycloud</userinput>, bo uporabil "
"poverilnice iz zgornjega razdelka <literal>[mycloud]</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If no profiles are configured, KIO S3 uses the default AWS credentials "
"chain, which includes environment variables (<envar>AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID</"
"envar>, <envar>AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY</envar>), the <literal>[default]</"
"literal> section in <filename>~/.aws/credentials</filename>, and EC2 "
"instance roles."
msgstr ""
"Če ni konfiguriranega nobenega profila, KIO S3 uporabi privzeto verigo "
"poverilnic AWS, ki vključuje okoljske spremenljivke "
"(<envar>AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID</envar>, <envar>AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY</envar>), "
"razdelek <literal>[default]</literal> v <filename>~/.aws/credentials</"
"filename> in vloge pojavka EC2."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can optionally set the region using <filename>~/.aws/config</filename>:"
msgstr ""
"Regijo lahko po želji nastavite z uporabo <filename>~/.aws/config</filename>:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[default]\n"
"region = eu-west-1\n"
"\n"
"[profile mycloud]\n"
"region = auto"
msgstr ""
"[default]\n"
"region = eu-west-1\n"
"\n"
"[profile mycloud]\n"
"region = auto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <filename>~/.aws/config</filename>, named profiles use the "
"<literal>profile</literal> prefix (&eg; <literal>[profile mycloud]</"
"literal>), while in <filename>~/.aws/credentials</filename> the prefix is "
"not used (&eg; <literal>[mycloud]</literal>). This is a convention of the "
"AWS SDK."
msgstr ""
"V <filename>~/.aws/config</filename> imenovani profili uporabljajo predpono "
"<literal>profile</literal> (npr. <literal>[profile mycloud]</literal>), "
"medtem ko se v <filename>~/.aws/credentials</filename> predpona ne uporablja "
"(npr. <literal>[mycloud]</literal>). To je konvencija AWS SDK."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "URL Scheme"
msgstr "Shema URL"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"KIO S3 uses the <literal>s3://</literal> URL scheme. You can type these URLs "
"directly in the <application>Dolphin</application> location bar or use them "
"with command-line tools such as <command>kioclient</command>."
msgstr ""
"KIO S3 uporablja shemo URL-jev <literal>s3://</literal>. Te URL-je lahko "
"vnesete neposredno v naslovno vrstico <application>Dolphin</application> ali "
"pa jih uporabite z orodji ukazne vrstice, kot je <command>kioclient</"
"command>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "s3://"
msgstr "s3://"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists all buckets available with the default AWS credentials."
msgstr "Navede vse razpoložljive vedra s privzetimi poverilnicami AWS."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "s3://<replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>/"
msgstr "s3://<replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>/"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists the contents of <replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>."
msgstr "Navede vsebino <replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"s3://<replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>/<replaceable>path/to/file.txt</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"s3://<replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>/<replaceable>path/to/file.txt</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accesses a specific file in the bucket."
msgstr "Dostopi do določene datoteke v vedru."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "s3://@<replaceable>profile</replaceable>/"
msgstr "s3://@<replaceable>profile</replaceable>/"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists all buckets available on the named profile."
msgstr "Navede vse vedra, ki so na voljo v imenovanem profilu."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"s3://<replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>@<replaceable>profile</replaceable>/"
msgstr ""
"s3://<replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>@<replaceable>profile</replaceable>/"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lists the contents of <replaceable>mybucket</replaceable> on the named "
"profile."
msgstr ""
"Navede vsebino <replaceable>mybucket</replaceable> v imenovanem profilu."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"s3://<replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>@<replaceable>profile</replaceable>/"
"<replaceable>path/to/file.txt</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"s3://<replaceable>mybucket</replaceable>@<replaceable>profile</replaceable>/"
"<replaceable>path/to/file.txt</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accesses a specific file on the named profile."
msgstr "Dostopa do določene datoteke v imenovanem profilu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you add a profile in <guilabel>System Settings</guilabel>, a shortcut "
"is automatically created in the <application>Dolphin</application> Places "
"panel. You can simply click it to browse that profile's buckets."
msgstr ""
"Ko v <guilabel>Sistemske nastavitve</guilabel> dodate profil, se v plošči "
"Mesta v <application>Dolphin</application> samodejno ustvari bližnjica. Za "
"brskanje po vedrih tega profila ga preprosto kliknite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing Files"
msgstr "Brskanje po datotekah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open <application>Dolphin</application> and type <userinput>s3://</"
"userinput> in the location bar to see your S3 buckets. Click a bucket to "
"browse its contents. Folders and files appear just like on a local "
"filesystem."
msgstr ""
"Odprite <application>Dolphin</application> in v naslovno vrstico vnesite "
"<userinput>s3://</userinput>, da si ogledate svoje vedre S3. Kliknite vedro, "
"da si ogledate njegovo vsebino. Mape in datoteke so prikazane tako kot v "
"lokalnem datotečnem sistemu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To browse a specific profile, type <userinput>s3://@<replaceable>profile</"
"replaceable>/</userinput> or click the profile shortcut in the Places panel."
msgstr ""
"Če želite brskati po določenem profilu, vnesite <userinput>s3://"
"@<replaceable>profile</replaceable>/</userinput> ali kliknite bližnjico "
"profila na plošči Mesta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigation works as expected: you can use the breadcrumb bar, the back and "
"forward buttons, and the location bar. You can also open S3 locations in new "
"tabs."
msgstr ""
"Navigacija deluje po pričakovanjih: lahko uporabite vrstico s sledilnimi "
"drobtinami, gumba nazaj in naprej ter lokacijsko vrstico. Lokacije S3 lahko "
"odprete tudi v novih zavihkih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Operations"
msgstr "Operacije z datotekami"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Uploading Files"
msgstr "Prenos datotek tja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag files from your local filesystem and drop them into an S3 folder in "
"<application>Dolphin</application>. You can also use copy and paste. Large "
"files are automatically uploaded using multipart upload to avoid excessive "
"memory usage."
msgstr ""
"Povlecite datoteke iz lokalnega datotečnega sistema in jih spustite v mapo "
"S3 v <application>Dolphin</application>. Uporabite lahko tudi kopiranje in "
"lepljenje. Velike datoteke se samodejno naložijo z večdelnim nalaganjem, da "
"se prepreči prekomerna poraba pomnilnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Downloading Files"
msgstr "Prenos datotek sem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag files from an S3 folder to a local folder, or use copy and paste. You "
"can also open S3 files directly in applications — the file will be "
"downloaded to a temporary location and opened."
msgstr ""
"Povlecite datoteke iz mape S3 v lokalno mapo ali uporabite kopiranje in "
"lepljenje. Datoteke S3 lahko odprete tudi neposredno v aplikacijah – "
"datoteka se bo prenesla na začasno lokacijo in odprla."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copying"
msgstr "Kopiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can copy files within the same S3 service using copy and paste or drag "
"and drop. The copy is performed server-side, so it does not require "
"downloading and re-uploading the file."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke lahko kopirate znotraj iste storitve S3 s kopiranjem in lepljenjem "
"ali povleci in spusti. Kopiranje se izvede na strani strežnika, zato ni "
"treba prenesti in ponovno naložiti datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Renaming"
msgstr "Preimenovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycap>F2</keycap> in <application>Dolphin</application> to rename a "
"file or folder. Since S3 does not have a native rename operation, KIO S3 "
"performs a server-side copy to the new name and then deletes the original. "
"For folders, all files inside the folder are copied and deleted individually."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycap>F2</keycap> v <application>Dolphin</application>, da "
"preimenujete datoteko ali mapo. Ker S3 nima izvorne operacije preimenovanja, "
"KIO S3 izvede kopiranje na strani strežnika z novim imenom in nato izbriše "
"izvirnik. Pri mapah se vse datoteke v mapi kopirajo in izbrišejo posamično."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting"
msgstr "Brisanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select files or folders and press <keycap>Delete</keycap>. When deleting a "
"folder, all files and subfolders inside it are deleted recursively."
msgstr ""
"Izberite datoteke ali mape in pritisnite <keycap>Izbriši</keycap>. Pri "
"brisanju mape se rekurzivno izbrišejo vse datoteke in podmape v njej."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating Folders"
msgstr "Kreiranje map"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycap>F10</keycap> or use <menuchoice><guimenu>Create New</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Folder...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to create a new folder "
"inside a bucket."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycap>F10</keycap> ali uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Ustvari "
"novo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mapo ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da "
"ustvarite novo mapo znotraj vedra."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Multiple Profiles"
msgstr "Delo z več profili"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use several S3-compatible services (for example, one for backups and "
"another for website assets), you can configure a profile for each one and "
"switch between them without changing any configuration files or environment "
"variables."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate več storitev, združljivih s S3 (na primer eno za varnostne "
"kopije in drugo za sredstva spletnega mesta), lahko za vsako konfigurirate "
"profil in preklapljate med njimi, ne da bi spremenili konfiguracijske "
"datoteke ali spremenljivke okolja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each profile appears as a separate shortcut in the <application>Dolphin</"
"application> Places panel. Clicking a profile shortcut shows the buckets "
"available on that service. All operations (upload, download, copy, rename, "
"delete) work independently within each profile."
msgstr ""
"Vsak profil se prikaže kot ločena bližnjica v plošči Mesta v programu "
"<application>Dolphin</application>. S klikom na bližnjico profila se "
"prikažejo vedra, ki so na voljo v tej storitvi. Vse operacije (nalaganje, "
"prenos, kopiranje, preimenovanje, brisanje) delujejo neodvisno znotraj "
"vsakega profila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copying or renaming files between different profiles is not supported. S3 "
"server-side copy only works within a single service. To move files between "
"profiles, copy them to a local folder first, then upload to the other "
"profile."
msgstr ""
"Kopiranje ali preimenovanje datotek med različnimi profili ni podprto. "
"Kopiranje na strani strežnika S3 deluje samo znotraj ene storitve. Če želite "
"premikati datoteke med profili, jih najprej kopirajte v lokalno mapo in nato "
"naložite v drug profil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Known Limitations"
msgstr "Znane omejitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bucket creation and deletion are not supported. Use the provider's web "
"console or CLI tools to manage buckets."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje in brisanje veder ni podprto. Za upravljanje veder uporabite "
"spletno konzolo ponudnika ali orodja CLI."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"File permissions shown in <application>Dolphin</application> are cosmetic. "
"S3 uses its own access control model (IAM policies and bucket policies), "
"which does not map to Unix permissions."
msgstr ""
"Dovoljenja za datoteke, prikazana v <application>Dolphin</application>, so "
"kozmetična. S3 uporablja svoj model nadzora dostopa (pravilniki IAM in "
"pravilniki bucket), ki se ne preslika v dovoljenja Unixa."

#~ msgid "2021-01-05"
#~ msgstr "05.01.2021"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "KIO S3 allows you to list Amazon S3 buckets and objects, to upload files "
#~ "and folders to a bucket and to delete objects from a bucket. You can also "
#~ "copy folders or objects within S3, as well as move or rename objects."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "KIO S3 vam omogoča, da navedete vedra in predmete Amazon S3, naložite "
#~ "datoteke in mape v vedro in izbrišete predmete iz vedra. Prav tako lahko "
#~ "kopirate mape ali predmete znotraj S3, pa tudi premikate ali preimenujete "
#~ "predmete."

#~ msgid "You can use the s3 KIO worker like this:"
#~ msgstr "Delavca s3 KIO lahko uporabite takole:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<userinput>s3://</userinput> or <userinput>s3://<replaceable>mybucket/"
#~ "mykey</replaceable></userinput>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<userinput>s3://</userinput> ali <userinput>s3://<replaceable>mybucket/"
#~ "mykey</replaceable></userinput>."

#~ msgid "The first URL shows all your S3 buckets."
#~ msgstr "Prvi URL prikazuje vsa vaša vedra S3."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The URL <userinput>s3://<replaceable>mybucket/mykey</replaceable></"
#~ "userinput> lists all the files and folders from your <userinput>mybucket</"
#~ "userinput> bucket."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "URL <userinput>s3://<replaceable>mybucket/mykey</replaceable></userinput> "
#~ "navaja vse datoteke in mape iz vašega vedra <userinput>mybucket</"
#~ "userinput>."
